      "title": "COVID on the rise again, health officials",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Health officials have warned of a possible rise of COVID-19 again in Sri Lanla.",
        "On Sunday (17) the number of confirmed COVID-19 infections was 34, however, there were NO deaths.",
        "The number of confirmed COVID-19 infections by now is 664,414."
      ],
